WHAT IS RIVALS

The Rivals crypto community is made up of animal lovers who believe in leaving the world better than we found it. A gaming universe that fosters competition, friendship and sharing, learning, and playful challenges paired with a big heart. It is a multi-purpose token that serves a purpose that is not only fun, but also worthwhile. First of its kind, it tackles a growing problem around the world in a novel way: the overcrowding and underfunding of animal shelters. Through its play-to-earn model, Rivals Gaming Universe hopes to encourage crypto participation and continue to rally ongoing support and enjoyment while coupling that support with a donate utility, voting rights, competitions, incredible merchandise, a hilarious animated series, and much more.

website : https://rivals.io/
